#!/usr/bin/env bash
#### MainsailOS Specific Tweaks for armbian images
####
#### Written by Stephan Wendel aka KwadFan <me@stephanwe.de>
#### Copyright 2023 - till today
#### https://github.com/mainsail-crew/MainsailOS
